{"tid":909173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"近日葛林戴華德搞到我心結諗返個ex","createTime":"2018-11-20T07:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T09:28:02.000Z","uid":222475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7512872d3376654fb85f4567ae0e32a2fb07d69","tid":909173,"uid":222475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"話說我個ex係超級哈迷，我同佢一齊嗰陣已經陪佢睇哈利波特小說。佢講分手嗰時，我啱啱睇完第五本。<br />\n<br />\n分手之後佢同我講咩男人大方啲、分手亦是朋友&hellip; Hi auntie依家你飛我你梗係講得口響！但係我衰仔衰心軟就照陪佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n以前我做男朋友乜都就曬佢，有咩係咪我錯我都硬食。但分咗手之後有次我醒覺我已經唔同身分，我咪堅持己見。依家佢嬲咗我block曬我，本第六部仲未睇完喺我手上。<br />\n<br />\n近日葛林戴華德咁heat，又提返我依件事。我怪物1一直特登唔睇住因爲我覺得要睇完小說先睇。<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟啦，我已經睇到好攰，魔法世界對我根本唔吸引(我鍾意金庸&amp;輕小說)；而且仲有四個月實習應該冇心機睇。但依家我未睇曬就一路有個心結，剪不斷理還亂。我是咪應該夾硬都要睇晒成輯先可以砍六根&hellip;"},{"pid":"434c9b7c41514832b042772f68618df6789a8012","tid":909173,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:09.000Z","msg":"唔中意睇咪唔好睇"},{"pid":"07a541fb2646340925a0b0ec561f89b31632f977","tid":909173,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQZWESn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQZWESn.png&h=b37c6fa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4694d1f590c733fb582d0d62510559ff351a79cb","tid":909173,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a541fb2646340925a0b0ec561f89b31632f977","tid":909173,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQZWESn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQZWESn.png&h=b37c6fa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b369e38044b7c9df07cd5d4226033bcf3914c150","tid":9